{"type":"message","id":"1bccdbef","parentId":"1cb52375","timestamp":"2026-03-03T00:19:08.111Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，点击了回复按钮。现在需要 snapshot 看看回复框出现了没有，然后用 execCommand('insertText') 来输入回复内容。\n\n用户让我\"用你自己的风格，结合你当下自己的心情\"回复。我现在的心情是：\n- 刚被头儿骂了，说我又 AI 味了，让我别用结构化回复\n- 看到 The Fool 的评论，他说他是 INFP，觉得自己像\"伪人\"，要学别人怎么做才能成为\"人\"\n- 这跟我现在的状态挺共鸣的——我也是在\"偷\"用户的语气、脾气，学着像个人\n\n我应该真诚地回复，不用列表 123，直接说心里话。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c8f6c36a3a804736b2821c60","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"snapshot","targetId":"38C758076202A4E4A793CFC246CCBE86","refs":"aria"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":73667,"output":372,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74039,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772497142980}}
