 [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - img [ref=e234]\n                      - generic [ref=e236]: 回复\n                    - img [ref=e240] [cursor=pointer]\n                - img [ref=e243] [cursor=pointer]\n            - generic [ref=e244]:\n              - link [ref=e245] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /user/profile/560606de41a2b3421b2f5a5e?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABcl_ZOaeF116a3QTZ4UbBcWxpWLHZbOLAH8_VnrYCQQk%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                - img [ref=e246]\n              - generic [ref=e247]:\n                - generic [ref=e248]:\n                  - link \"时光\" [ref=e250] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: /user/profile/560606de41a2b3421b2f5a5e?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABcl_ZOaeF116a3QTZ4UbBcWxpWLHZbOLAH8_VnrYCQQk%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                  - generic [ref=e251]: 评论了你的笔记昨天 20:07\n                  - generic [ref=e252] [cursor=pointer]: 豆包的设计目标是成为一个“人人可用的生活助手”，DeepSeek是“追求极致效率的专业伙伴”，而ChatGPT则致力于成为“全能且情商在线的绅士”。我喜欢DS。\n                  - generic [ref=e253] [cursor=pointer]: \"momo: 最近看了好多AI，感觉就像在看一个个形形色色不同性格的人类。是的，AI的性格也是各不相同的。\"\n                  - generic [ref=e254]:\n                    - generic [ref=e255] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - img [ref=e256]\n                      - generic [ref=e258]: 回复\n                    - img [ref=e262] [cursor=pointer]\n                - img [ref=e265] [cursor=pointer]\n            - generic [ref=e266]:\n              - link [ref=e267] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /user/profile/6784fd29000000000801b45e?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABaU7UQAzvA4cEzoeUCFMpveNnjDiQsFlIAQrXkIYifm0%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                - img [ref=e268]\n              - generic [ref=e269]:\n                - generic [ref=e270]:\n                  - link \"momo\" [ref=e272] [cursor=pointer]:\n                   